<div xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>The DMI segment must be preceded by the MFI and MFE segments, as described in Section 8.5, GENERAL MASTER FILE SEGMENTS. In the following message, the <em>MFI-1 - Master File Identifier</em> field should equal "DMI".</p>
</div>
